1258  if (foundValidProfile) {
1259  int16_t nonElevFirstChirpIdx = -1;
1260  for (chirpLoopIdx=0;chirpLoopIdx<frameTotalChirps;chirpLoopIdx++)
1261  {
1262  bool validChirpHasElevation=false;
1263  bool validChirpHasOneTxPerChirp=false;
1264  uint16_t chirpTxEn = validChirpTxEnBits[chirpLoopIdx];
1265  if (chirpTxEn == 0) {
1266  /* this profile doesnt have all the needed chirps */
1267  foundValidProfile = false;
1268  break;
1269  }
1270  /* check if this is an elevation TX chirp */
1271  validChirpHasElevation = (chirpTxEn==0x2);
1272  validProfileHasElevation |= validChirpHasElevation;
1273  /* if not, then check the MIMO config */
1274  if (!validChirpHasElevation)
1275  {
1276  validChirpHasOneTxPerChirp = ((chirpTxEn==0x1) || (chirpTxEn==0x4));
1277  /* if this is the first chirp without elevation, record the chirp's
1278  MIMO config as profile's MIMO config. We dont handle intermix
1279  at this point */
1280  if (nonElevFirstChirpIdx==-1) {
1281  validProfileHasOneTxPerChirp = validChirpHasOneTxPerChirp;
1282  nonElevFirstChirpIdx = chirpLoopIdx;
1283  }
1284  /* check the chirp's MIMO config against Profile's MIMO config */
1285  if (validChirpHasOneTxPerChirp != validProfileHasOneTxPerChirp)
1286  {
1287  /* this profile doesnt have all chirps with same MIMO config */
1288  foundValidProfile = false;
1289  break;
1290  }
1291  }
1292  /* save the antennas actually enabled in this profile */
1293  validProfileTxEn |= chirpTxEn;
1294  }
1295  }
1296 
1297  /* found valid chirps for the frame; mark this profile valid */
1298  if (foundValidProfile==true) {
1299  rlProfileCfg_t profileCfg;
1300  uint32_t numTxAntAzim = 0;
1301  uint32_t numTxAntElev = 0;
1302 
1303  dataPathObj->validProfileIdx = profileLoopIdx;
1304  dataPathObj->numTxAntennas = 0;
1305  if (validProfileHasElevation)
1306  {
1307  numTxAntElev = 1;
1308  }
1309  if (!validProfileHasOneTxPerChirp)
1310  {
1311  numTxAntAzim=1;
1312  }
1313  else
1314  {
1315  if (validProfileTxEn & 0x1)
1316  {
1317  numTxAntAzim++;
1318  }
1319  if (validProfileTxEn & 0x4)
1320  {
1321  numTxAntAzim++;
1322  }
1323  }
1324  /*System_printf("Azimuth Tx: %d (MIMO:%d), Elev Tx:%d\n",
1325  numTxAntAzim,validProfileHasMIMO,numTxAntElev);*/
1326  dataPathObj->numTxAntennas = numTxAntAzim + numTxAntElev;
1327  dataPathObj->numVirtualAntAzim = numTxAntAzim * dataPathObj->numRxAntennas;
1328  dataPathObj->numVirtualAntElev = numTxAntElev * dataPathObj->numRxAntennas;
1329  dataPathObj->numVirtualAntennas = dataPathObj->numVirtualAntAzim + dataPathObj->numVirtualAntElev;
1330 
1331  /* Sanity Check: Ensure that the number of antennas is within system limits */
1332  MmwDemo_debugAssert (dataPathObj->numVirtualAntennas > 0);
1333  MmwDemo_debugAssert (dataPathObj->numVirtualAntennas <= (SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL));
1334 
1335  /* Copy the Rx channel compensation coefficients from common area to data path structure */
1336  if (validProfileHasOneTxPerChirp)
1337  {
1338  for (i = 0; i < dataPathObj->numTxAntennas; i++)
1339  {
1340  txAntOrder[i] = log2Approx(validChirpTxEnBits[i]);
1341  }
1342  for (txIdx = 0; txIdx < dataPathObj->numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
1343  {
1344  for (rxIdx = 0; rxIdx < dataPathObj->numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
1345  {
1346  dataPathObj->compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[txIdx*dataPathObj->numRxAntennas + rxIdx] =
1347  dataPathObj->cliCommonCfg->compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[txAntOrder[txIdx]*SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL + rxAntOrder[rxIdx]];
1348 
1349  }
1350 
1351  }
1352  }
1353  else
1354  {
1355  cmplx16ImRe_t one;
1356  one.imag = 0;
1357  one.real = 0x7fff;
1358  for (txIdx = 0; txIdx < dataPathObj->numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
1359  {
1360  for (rxIdx = 0; rxIdx < dataPathObj->numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
1361  {
1362  dataPathObj->compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[txIdx*dataPathObj->numRxAntennas + rxIdx] = one;
1363  }
1364 
1365  }
1366  }
1367 
1368  /* Get the profile configuration: */
1369  if (MMWave_getProfileCfg(profileHandle,&profileCfg, &errCode) < 0)
1370  {
1371  MmwDemo_debugAssert(0);
1372  return false;
1373  }
1374 
1375 #ifndef MMW_ENABLE_NEGATIVE_FREQ_SLOPE
1376  /* Check frequency slope */
1377  if (profileCfg.freqSlopeConst < 0)
1378  {
1379  System_printf("Frequency slope must be positive\n");
1380  MmwDemo_debugAssert(0);
1381  }
1382 #endif
1383 
1384  dataPathObj->numAdcSamples = profileCfg.numAdcSamples;
1385  dataPathObj->numRangeBins = MmwDemo_pow2roundup(dataPathObj->numAdcSamples);
1386  dataPathObj->numChirpsPerFrame = frameTotalChirps *
1387  gMmwMCB.cfg.ctrlCfg.u.frameCfg.frameCfg.numLoops;
1388 
1389  dataPathObj->numAngleBins = MMW_NUM_ANGLE_BINS;
1390  dataPathObj->numDopplerBins = dataPathObj->numChirpsPerFrame/dataPathObj->numTxAntennas;
1391  dataPathObj->numRangeBinsPerTransfer = MMW_NUM_RANGE_BINS_PER_TRANSFER;
1392  dataPathObj->rangeResolution = MMWDEMO_SPEED_OF_LIGHT_IN_METERS_PER_SEC * profileCfg.digOutSampleRate * 1e3 /
1393  (2 * profileCfg.freqSlopeConst * ((3.6*1e3*900)/(1U << 26)) * 1e12 * dataPathObj->numRangeBins);
1394 
1395  dataPathObj->xyzOutputQFormat = (uint32_t) ceil(log10(16./fabs(dataPathObj->rangeResolution))/log10(2));
1396  dataPathObj->dataPathMode = DATA_PATH_WITH_ADCBUF;
1397  dataPathObj->frameStartIntCounter = 0;
1398  dataPathObj->interFrameProcToken = 0;
1399  }
1400  }
1401  return foundValidProfile;
1402 }
